Salda () is a rural locality (a selo) in Chorodinsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Salda is located 31&nbsp;km southeast of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Choroda is the nearest rural locality.
